    • Shoe

      public Shoe(Kind kind, Color color, Brand brand, double size)
      Creates a new Shoe instance.
      参数:
      kind - the kind of shoe (e.g., SNEAKER, DRESS)
      color - the color (e.g., BLACK, PASTEL)
      brand - the brand (e.g., NIKE, ADIDAS)
      size - the size (e.g., 8.5)
      抛出:
      IllegalArgumentException - if brand == NIKE && kind == DRESS
